flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens content management area] --> B[View list of records]
    B --> C{Action?}
    C -->|Create| D[Open create form]
    C -->|Edit| E[Open edit form]
    C -->|Delete| F[Request delete confirmation]
    D --> G[Submit form]
    E --> G
    G --> H[Validate data]
    H --> I{Valid?}
    I -->|No| J[Show validation errors]
    I -->|Yes| K[Save record]
    F --> L{Confirmed and allowed?}
    L -->|No| J
    L -->|Yes| M[Delete record]
    K --> N[Refresh list]
    M --> N